BMPANEL2 THEME - twily.info


install theme files to "~/.local/share/bmpanel2/themes/twily/*"

follow the patching instructions in "_PATCHLOG_TWILY"

execute bmpanel2 with --theme=twily



-------------------------

images / gimp settings for {bg,separtor_wide}

    drop shadow
        offset x 0
        offset y 3
        blur radius 23
        color rgb(7,7,10) #07070A
        opacity: 75
        no resizing

    crop image inside outline
